<subSubSection id="C32A651BFF8A5F2EFF5CFA6F0C49F9E2" pageId="6" pageNumber="135" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B8F3690FF8A5F2EFF5CFA6F0C49F9E2" blockId="6.[151,1127,1378,1562]" pageId="6" pageNumber="135">
<emphasis id="B944EA82FF8A5F2EFF5CFA6F0936FA62" bold="true" box="[151,281,1410,1433]" pageId="6" pageNumber="135">Comments.</emphasis>
The species, originally published as 
<taxonomicName id="4C304D13FF8A5F2EFD67FA6E0BA7FA61" authorityName="Pic" authorityYear="1916" box="[684,904,1410,1434]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Baeocera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="135" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="discoidale">
<emphasis id="B944EA82FF8A5F2EFD67FA6E0BA7FA61" box="[684,904,1410,1434]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="135">Baeocera discoidale</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
[sic] Pic, 1916, was redescribed and transferred to 
<taxonomicName id="4C304D13FF8A5F2EFE15FA4F0A70FA41" authorityName="Leach" authorityYear="1815" box="[478,607,1442,1466]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Scaphisoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="135" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B944EA82FF8A5F2EFE15FA4F0A70FA41" box="[478,607,1442,1466]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="135">Scaphisoma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFA14B61FF8A5F2EFD43FA4F0B20FA42" author="LOBL I." box="[648,783,1442,1465]" pageId="6" pageNumber="135" pagination="149 - 160" refId="ref8433" refString="LOBL I. 1973: Uber einige orientalische Scaphidiidae (Coleoptera) aus dem Museo Civico di Storia Naturale di Genova und Museum National d'Histoire Naturelle de Paris. Nouvelle Revue d'Entomologie 3: 149 - 160." type="journal article" year="1973">LÖBL (1973)</bibRefCitation>
. It was given the new substitute name of 
<taxonomicName id="4C304D13FF8A5F2EFF38FA2F091BFA22" authorityName="Lobl" authorityYear="1979" box="[243,308,1474,1497]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Scaphisoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="135" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pici">
<emphasis id="B944EA82FF8A5F2EFF38FA2F091BFA22" box="[243,308,1474,1497]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="135">S. pici</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFA14B61FF8A5F2EFE90FA2F09F0FA22" author="LOBL I." box="[347,479,1474,1497]" pageId="6" pageNumber="135" pagination="77 - 129" refId="ref8471" refString="LOBL I. 1979: Die Scaphidiidae (Coleoptera) Sudindiens. Revue Suisse de Zoologie 86: 77 - 129." type="journal article" year="1979">LÖBL (1979)</bibRefCitation>
, because of secondary homonymy with 
<taxonomicName id="4C304D13FF8A5F2EFC4DFA2F08E0FA02" authority="Achard, 1915" authorityName="Achard" authorityYear="1915" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Baeocera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="135" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="discoidale">
<emphasis id="B944EA82FF8A5F2EFC4DFA2F0C22FA21" box="[902,1037,1474,1498]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="135">S. discoidale</emphasis>
Achard, 1915
</taxonomicName>
, placed in synonymy with 
<taxonomicName id="4C304D13FF8A5F2EFE2FFA0F0AD1FA02" authority="Achard, 1915" authorityName="Achard" authorityYear="1915" box="[484,766,1506,1530]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Scaphisoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="135" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="binotatum">
<emphasis id="B944EA82FF8A5F2EFE2FFA0F0A46FA01" box="[484,617,1506,1530]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="135">S. binotatum</emphasis>
Achard, 1915
</taxonomicName>
. Currently, only the single original female specimen of 
<taxonomicName id="4C304D13FF8A5F2EFEA4F9EF0A31F9E2" authorityName="Lobl" authorityYear="1979" box="[367,542,1538,1562]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Scaphisoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="135" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pici">
<emphasis id="B944EA82FF8A5F2EFEA4F9EF0A31F9E2" box="[367,542,1538,1562]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="135">Scaphisoma pici</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is known. It was held for the 
<typeStatus id="548B8832FF8A5F2EFC97F9EF0B96F9E2" box="[860,953,1538,1561]" pageId="6" pageNumber="135">holotype</typeStatus>
in 
<bibRefCitation id="EFA14B61FF8A5F2EFC10F9EF0C4DF9E2" author="LOBL I." box="[987,1122,1538,1561]" pageId="6" pageNumber="135" pagination="149 - 160" refId="ref8433" refString="LOBL I. 1973: Uber einige orientalische Scaphidiidae (Coleoptera) aus dem Museo Civico di Storia Naturale di Genova und Museum National d'Histoire Naturelle de Paris. Nouvelle Revue d'Entomologie 3: 149 - 160." type="journal article" year="1973">LÖBL (1973)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
